rComments: He is so awesome! His class is very interesting. Get the study guide, you will be fine for all the exams! good luck!

Really nice guy, but he's extremely old fashion. Doesn't use any new technology. Even your grades will be posted on a sheet of paper pinned to a wall. That being said, he's a very good teacher and knows his material well.

Decent guy overall. Knows the material well. However, indicates that he can be reached outside of class for certain things such as obtaining exam marks and then doesn't answer emails. Pay close attention to material covered in class but not in the textbook.
Great man but he does not prepare you well enough for the final (which is prepared by the psych dept and NOT him).
AWESOME best prof you'll ever have!! Super nice and helpful, and prepares you very well for the final. I wish he could teach all my courses! </3
so chill, makes funny references, great class, study guide was super helpful
AMAZING. Not enough good words to describe Markow.
really good. really really good. a bit intimidating @ office hours, but EXTREMELY knowledgeable and easy to understand!

He has very good examples to make students understand concepts, and definately knows what he is talking about. The lectures are very interesting, midterms are hard...you really need to pay attention to everything he says. Has a good sense of humor and can crack some good jokes!
He thought me A LOT!... He influenced a Huge part of my life!
Had him for both 1101 and 1102. Best Psych classes I've ever taken. Overall, he was the best professor I have ever had. He lecture style is quite structured as well as results oriented.
Great teacher with clear and detailed explanations. Easy to follow and understand. Very patient with stragglers.
Never bored in his class!  The 3 hours zip right by and his lectures are easy to follow and make easy to understand notes.

BY far the best prof at U of O. I agree with what has been said: he is entertaining, makes coming to class a joy,and I have learned more from him than from any other prof. Unfortunately, he set the bar so high, I have been repeatedly dissapointed by other profs ever since! I think all profs should sit in on a lecture with him to see how its done!
This teacher is hilarious and easy to understand. I didnt mind taking his 7-10 pm class just to have him as a psychology teacher again.
Richard Markow is the product of a secret government experiment to create the ultimate professor...He's the best.
Funny prof, his constant comments and "tips" to help us all pick up while still pertaining to psychology keep it interesting. going to minor in psych because of him.
Amazing Professor! No previous interest in Psychology but I'm definitely taking every possible class with him! Attendance isn't mandatory - but you actually want to show up
Funny guy and makes the class interesting. Keeps you awake even in the 7-10pm Thursday night class. If only all profs were like him....

By far the best professor I have had thus far. No doubt about it. Markow is a genious in his field and makes subject matter accessible and intriguing for students. Never was I bored or asleep in his 7-10pm psych lectures. Had great stories and examples for just about every concept taught--made a world of difference in memorization and interest.

Very nice prof. Obviously loves his work. Informative, and manages to keep the attention of first years during entire three-hour evening lectures. Can be very funny. When I was sick last year, I had no problems whatsoever with having my midterm put off until I was better. Nice guy.
Makes the material interesting, easy to listen to. Definitely taking another class taught by him next semester!
AMAZING PROF...possibly the best ever!!!
He's great!
possibly the only good prof at Ottawa U... I'm only in second year, but Markow so far is the only prof that was good overall in all aspects of teaching and testing.
The best. Super-clear about what needs to be known and extremely good at portraying the material. He makes the textbook look bad. Good examples, funny jokes, an all-around fun time from 7-10 PM.
Great professor, makes class interesting, It's very clear what you need to know and he gives you most of the info.
He's probably the best professor I have ever had for psychology or any subject for that matter. He made the entire year I had him exciting and interesting.
he knows a lot about applied psych, gave lots of examples. made clas so interesting! now i'm minoring in psych.
Markow is a clear, organized, and engaging lecturer. He knows his stuff, understands what students need, and has a good sense of humour. I'd love to take more courses with him.
Great Prof. overall. Very clear in his explanations, with no misconceptions. Come to class and you will have an easy course.

Great prof. Always seems enthusiastic about the topics he's discussing and explains things very well. Most of the midterms are textbook based but he slips in a few of his own notes too. I had him 7-10 on a Thursday and he kept me paying attention the whole time. LOVED this prof! Easy exams (minimal studying needed).

I don't know why everyone loves this prof so much. I took his class expecting him to be great but to be honest he was kind of a drone. He focuses on the interesting topics, but he still managed to make it boring. The final is only based on textbook material, so read it because he won't prepare you for it in class.
awesome
good prof, funny guy a little awkward during office hours... :/.

Great Prof. Speaks fluently and explains every theory with detail and explains them with situations students can relate to. It's like watching Einstein explain cognitive theories rather than quantum physics.

hes amazing, makes lectures super entertaining even at 7-10pm.  Great teaching style, he only jots pt on the board but speak clearly n slowly enuf for great notes to be taken.  Very approachable with questions.  Great life experiences so always have funny anecdotes or comments to make u laugh

This prof rocks!.....my fav so far.  I love his teaching style.  He actually uses the blackboard and doesn't just read off of slides.  He's so clear when he speaks making it really easy to grasp the material.  If I could take one of his classes again I definetly would.

Best prof I've had yet! He's clear, entertaining and captivating. If I hadn't already been interested in the subject he would have made me interested. HIGHLY recommended.

Really good prof!! I recommend any of his classes... he's super knowledgeable, knows something about everything... very clear, not extremely helpful one on one but you can easily understand everything just by going to class and reading the text. his 3 hour classes fly by.

This prof was fantastic. Fantastic. He is extremely knowledgeable on the subject, and he makes the 3 hour class go by fairly quickly because he is able to provide many helpful and clear examples to help you learn the material. He's also pretty funny, so take his class!
This prof is excellent.  Knows his stuff and delivers his lectures in a way that keeps the students interested and engaged.
class= waste of time. I got one word for this prof, "EW".
